- Child tax credits and family allowances (Family Bonus Plus)
- Mandatory health insurance thresholds
- Early retirement tax implications

Calculated as of December 31 of the tax year."""@en ;
        skos:note "Age as of December 31 of the tax year" .

:isAustrianResident rdf:type owl:DatatypeProperty ;
