- Business income plus rental income
- Any combination exceeding automatic withholding capabilities

Complexity increases tax compliance obligations and may affect available deductions."""@en ;
                          skos:note "Often triggers mandatory filing requirements under 2025 thresholds" .

:hasDeductions rdf:type owl:DatatypeProperty ;
