                                  rdfs:label "Lohnbezieher mit Zusatzeinkommen"@de ;
                                  rdfs:comment """Residents with wage tax liable income who also have additional income >€730 and total income >€14,517.

2025 Complex Threshold Rule: This captures the sophisticated interaction between wage and non-wage income:
1. Must have wage tax liable income (employment with withholding)
2. Must have additional non-wage income exceeding €730
3. Total combined income must exceed €14,517

This prevents automatic tax settlement through wage withholding and requires comprehensive assessment."""@en ;
                                  :legalBasis "EStG §42 Abs 1 (2025 combined income thresholds)" .

### Rule 3: Multiple employment holders must file if total >€14,517 (2025)
:MultipleEmploymentResident rdf:type owl:Class ;
