- Two or more non-self-employed jobs held simultaneously
- Multiple pension sources without joint tax deduction
- Combined employment income exceeding €14,517

Multiple income sources prevent accurate automatic tax withholding calculation."""@en ;
                            :legalBasis "EStG §42 Abs 1 (2025 multiple employment filing requirements)" .

### Rule 4: Self-employed entities must file regardless of income (Enhanced 2025)
:SelfEmployedEntity rdf:type owl:Class ;
