- Make quarterly advance payments if annual tax exceeds €3,900
- Maintain detailed business records and documentation
- File even for loss years to establish legal evidence for loss carryforwards

This applies to all categories of self-employed including new self-employed persons and freelancers."""@en ;
                    :legalBasis "EStG §42 Abs 1 Z 3 (Assessment obligation for self-employed), Electronic filing requirements" .

