- Use electronic submission preferred ('e-accounts')
- Comply with formal bookkeeping standards

This typically applies to larger businesses exceeding specific revenue or asset thresholds."""@en ;
                        :legalBasis "EStG §44 (Account-keeping and balance sheet attachment requirements)" .

